

{"id":5866,"date":"2023-11-21T09:55:20","date_gmt":"2023-11-21T02:55:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/tnt.locdt.site\/staging\/?p=5866"},"modified":"2023-11-21T10:33:31","modified_gmt":"2023-11-21T03:33:31","slug":"tro-lai-phong-tap-sau-mot-thoi-gian-dai-nghi-ngoi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/tro-lai-phong-tap-sau-mot-thoi-gian-dai-nghi-ngoi\/","title":{"rendered":"Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c, m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4937\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4937\" style=\"width: 1024px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-4937 size-large\" src=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-1024x520.png\" alt=\"t\u1eadp\" width=\"1024\" height=\"520\" srcset=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-1024x520.png 1024w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-300x152.png 300w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-768x390.png 768w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao-1536x780.png 1536w, https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/tang-cuong-tap-luyen-the-thao.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4937\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i<\/span><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>H\u00e3y th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c khi b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. V\u00ec \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea1n cho\u00e1ng ng\u1ee3p v\u00e0 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. H\u00e3y ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn v\u00e0 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n d\u1ea7n; n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea9y m\u00ecnh, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, h\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1edbi b\u00e1c s\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp. B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00eam.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>T\u00ecm b\u00e0i t\u1eadp b\u1ea1n th\u00edch<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, h\u00e3y t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng vi\u1ec7c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 tham gia m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n y\u00eau th\u00edch. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. Ch\u1ecdn m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft ho\u1eb7c h\u1ecfi xem m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham gia c\u00f9ng kh\u00f4ng. T\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n theo nh\u00f3m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn s\u1ebd \u00edt \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3 h\u01a1n l\u00e0 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp v\u1edbi c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e2u l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1edbp h\u1ecdc trong v\u00f2ng 30 ph\u00fat.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>\u0110\u1eebng qu\u00e1 kh\u1eaft khe v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp trong nhi\u1ec1u th\u00e1ng, th\u00ec vi\u1ec7c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh ho\u1eb7c s\u1ee9c b\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n gi\u1ea3m s\u00fat l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n l\u1ea1c quan \u2013 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i n\u01a1i b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u00e3y th\u1eed c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp d\u00e0nh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. Ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0m theo nh\u1eefng g\u1ee3i \u00fd sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>20 ph\u00fat r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u00e0 s\u0103n ch\u1eafc<\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u00a0 \u2013 h\u00e3y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00f3i quen c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c r\u00e8n luy\u1ec7n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f4 l\u1eadp c\u00e1c nh\u00f3m c\u01a1 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh. S\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1 \u0111\u01a1n, m\u00e1y m\u00f3c ho\u1eb7c tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u01a1 th\u1ec3 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>30 ph\u00fat t\u1eadp Cardio <\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u2013 t\u0103ng nh\u1ecbp tim c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp Cardio \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, cho d\u00f9 b\u1ea1n \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u00e1y ch\u1ea1y b\u1ed9, xe \u0111\u1ea1p, m\u00e1y tr\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebft hay m\u00e1y ch\u00e8o thuy\u1ec1n.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><b><i>10 ph\u00fat gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 <\/i><\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">\u2013 h\u00e3y gi\u00e3n c\u01a1 v\u00e0 th\u1ea3 l\u1ecfng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp v\u00ec n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n b\u1ecf t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u1ee9c m\u1ecfi c\u01a1 th\u1ec3.<\/span><\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb d\u1ee5ng c\u1ee5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n th\u1ee9c d\u1eady v\u00e0 th\u1ea5y gi\u00e0y t\u1eadp, \u00e1o hoodie, \u0111\u1ed3 \u0103n nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 b\u00ecnh n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thay v\u00ec l\u1eadp k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1eadp l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y bao nhi\u00eau bu\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t tu\u1ea7n, h\u00e3y \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. N\u1ebfu t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 x\u00e1ch m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc t\u00fai t\u1eadp v\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc ra kh\u1ecfi nh\u00e0, th\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd \u0111i t\u1eadp.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: #009fc2;\"><b>10 ph\u00fat l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7<\/b><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng h\u00e3y lu\u00f4n l\u1ea1c quan. B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n b\u1ea1n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch t\u1eadp m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat, d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 \u0111i b\u1ed9 10 ph\u00fat, b\u1ea1n \u0111ang c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng \u0111i v\u00e0 ng\u1eebng t\u1eadp, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1ecf qua c\u00e1c b\u00e0i t\u1eadp trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp sau th\u1eddi gian ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 ki\u00ean tr\u00ec. C\u00e1c <a href=\"https:\/\/thenewgym.vn\/5-ly-do-nen-tap-luyen-cung-huan-luyen-vien-ca-nhan\/\">hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n<\/a> c\u1ee7a The New Gym lu\u00f4n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 th\u00eam khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Ch\u00fac b\u1ea1n may m\u1eafn!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong>Th\u00f4ng tin li\u00ean h\u1ec7:<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/@thenewgymvn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Youtube The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/thenewgymvietnam\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Fanpage The New Gym<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">Hotline: 1900636920<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian d\u00e0i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u00f2ng t\u1eadp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c, m\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u00e3y th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n \u0110\u1eebng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng qu\u00e1 s\u1ee9c khi b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi b\u1eaft [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":5562,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[9],"t